One Paige box filled with Assorted files. A few are labeled, most are not. These Materials will need a finer sorting to be integrated in to the main portion of the collection.—Hosanna Banks (July 2000)
Two large flat Hollinger boxes have been added, they house several over sized items as well as all the materials that have been removed from frames.
There are 6 or 7 newly added Paige boxes that have not been had their preservation photocopies made and have not had their initial sort.
